author: sergeyli
msg: This completes migration to Neon 0.24 API, with two exceptions: SSL doesn't
work, and some tests produce a warning, "Test driver returned a status code."
* subversion/libsvn_ra_dav/util.c
(shim_endelm): when handling ELEM_unknown element, pass actual XML namespace
and element name into "old-style" endelm_cb handler. Remove whitespace
trimming for contents of all elements.

author: cmpilato
msg: Some code cleanups post-kfogel review, and little bug fix.
* subversion/libsvn_fs/tree.c
(find_youngest_copy): Rename 'loop_inc' to 'next_iter'.
(txn_body_history_prev): Move the checks for crossing copy history.
(svn_fs_history_t, assemble_history): Document these a little better.
* subversion/libsvn_repos/rev_hunt.c
(svn_repos_revisions_changed): Lose the subpool1 and subpool2 -- we
can do everything we need with just oldpool and newpool.  Also,
return specifics errors for invalid input revisions.
